sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Browser
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant AIS as AI Integration Service
    participant LLM as Stub / LM Studio Provider
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>FE: Select text and invoke AI action
    FE->>BE: POST /ai/rewrite|summarize|translate
    BE->>DB: Validate permissions, quota, base version
    BE->>DB: Create AI job (PENDING)
    BE-->>FE: { jobId, statusUrl, status }
    FE->>BE: Poll GET /ai/jobs/:jobId
    BE->>AIS: Run provider request with selected text snapshot
    AIS->>LLM: Prompt + scoped context
    LLM-->>AIS: Generated suggestion or failure
    AIS->>DB: Update job to SUCCEEDED/FAILED
    BE-->>FE: Job status + proposedText or error
    U->>FE: Apply all / apply selection / reject
    FE->>BE: PUT /documents/:id/content (AI-aware save)
    BE->>DB: Create version snapshots + persist content
